{"tid":189661,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"戲棚可唔可以唔好再開？","createTime":"2017-04-06T14:55:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-06T15:26:06.000Z","uid":98360,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"94b301560ea8b43eb9e9b5feccaba9b793f7b6b0","tid":189661,"uid":98360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T14:55:58.000Z","msg":"住戲棚附近，細個去青衣戲棚，野食又平又好食又唔太逼，至從早幾年比唔同咩食評埃豬同埋毒果報道，每到戲棚一開，逼撚滿哂人，野食變到又貴又難食，真係狗也不屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 最撚仆街一個二個搞撚到周地垃圾，大大個垃圾桶係出面唔掉，掉滿左就是但放係草叢就算，見住啲清潔啊姐逐個執番哂好辛苦，仲有就係一架架私家車泊係出面兩邊塞撚死哂，搞到條咁窄既路大塞車，出去定放工番屋企坐車經過個條路真係多得佢地唔少<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d78b95a2adc5d55343786c5c0f1a7e653f51f103","tid":189661,"uid":82829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T14:59:02.000Z","msg":"認同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6939058d554d33469303d6e35e123a8bcaf82188","tid":189661,"uid":98360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T14:59:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>認同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打都係附近<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？"},{"pid":"6119caa9ee19595a186d7657a33a1e6bb97c7e30","tid":189661,"uid":34209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T15:15:12.000Z","msg":"再係咁青衣陸沉啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2db955a1a49457ed5d13475753698efd7c1e6701","tid":189661,"uid":98360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T15:26:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>再係咁青衣陸沉啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n過多兩日就沉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}